Email Template Slicer
======================

An Email Template Slicer that helps create custom layouts for marketing emails.

You can try it out here: http://ferozemoh.github.io/

Current functionality
======================== 
The user can provide a url for the image in the textbox and click submit to 
render the image onto the slicing area. When the user clicks on any 
point in the slicing area, a horizontal line is drawn at that point. An existing line can be moved by selecting it and clicking the point where the line needs to be moved to.

Javascript library Paper.js is used for all things related to drawing.

